{"tid":1169702,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣好鐘意艾你老味","createTime":"2019-05-24T14:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T07:21:56.000Z","uid":197090,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"231c5ae8bf20c66aef5b97e6a2711c90d8fa48ef","tid":1169702,"uid":197090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:19:14.000Z","msg":"聖占士之鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n紐記legend<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zuZRKnr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzuZRKnr.png&h=5db0fc8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68fe5efd3efbf582436204575db7dd59a3d71dad","tid":1169702,"uid":197090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc3b779923b13b54cbb97c757b238a61432c342","tid":1169702,"uid":236108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:28:27.000Z","msg":"點解？ 有冇答案"},{"pid":"e208df91de48461f78d53b5977cbeae70acb9a58","tid":1169702,"uid":21544,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"鐘唔鐘意李斯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed29b30ce03b2c052b2d33ad4eb6a38ce70ab6c2","tid":1169702,"uid":36601,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"詩云：一生一志忠臣藏，看似天生蠢鈍兒。而立之年始開竅，成龍成虎未可知。 <br />\n<br />\n十月十六日，晴，與熱刺戰於聖占士。下半戰，熱刺勢稍佔優。統帥柏祖曰：貝斯既疲，何人以代之。忽一人出曰：俺願往。視之，老味背上２３號戰袍巍然挺立。曰：舊傷初愈，能戰否？對曰：必取敵將而還。 <br />\n<br />\n既出，一將趕來守之，乃舊將柏加也。柏加曰：汝運氣未足，且還再戰。曰：俺尚能謀。突然球來，老味左足絆右足，轟然倒地。裁判哨聲一響，紐卡素得一罰球。柏加大驚：君非吳下阿蒙矣！對曰：若敢輕俺，必十倍還之。 <br />\n<br />\n且戰至末段，紐卡素更勢益急。賴恩泰萊突彈球入禁區。老味機警閃開守衛，持球面對門將。門將費度心想：此角度必然要用左腳，老味左腳尤如殘廢，定必無虞。瞬間，老味揚起左腳，球似流星劃成彩虹直撲網窩，奇蹟為紐卡素挽頹成和。　曰：五年間每日反覆磨練左腳球技，始有此大成。 <br />\n<br />\n熱刺統帥哈利列納仰天長嘯：昔日廉頗七十救國，今日老味晚成大器。嗚呼，此君必為我爭歐聯資格之大患矣！遂吐血半升，昏厥倒地，半响方甦。"},{"pid":"7dbdcfbc6257354fbcf2f7171e7df0839967e8c8","tid":1169702,"uid":75028,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:36:23.000Z","msg":"人生就像紐卡素，愛過比拿美，愛過奧雲，愛過卡路爾，但是默默陪你到最後的，卻是艾你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d760acf76d883bf647a2284602068972c252479b","tid":1169702,"uid":85774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:36:44.000Z","msg":"淨係知佢好撚廢 佢細路又係廢 踢保頓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85efdb9c0ef1b47a8c3fc6fc87096307ab1790b","tid":1169702,"uid":197090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96501004502dde9f3a719a33349d0c469e895f5b","tid":1169702,"uid":156666,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"答案係!! 陳國邦 (李斯) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJebjw3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJebjw3.jpg&h=a0ee34e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2Laz5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2Laz5t.jpg&h=b15df2e2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n因為有人同你一樣好鐘意艾你老味係silly 癡線 冇可能會發生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSilly發音就係 see Li 斯李<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我地華人社會 習慣將last name 擺前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!! 答案就係李斯喇<img src=\"/assets/fa